des:
You can simply ask Alexa to control your Sendo products. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our "Sendo Smart" app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
(2) Configure our devices in "Sendo Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3) Enable "Sendo Smart" skill, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(4) Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
(5) Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, turn on air conditioner.
Alexa, turn off air conditioner.
Alexa, set air conditioner to heat mode.
Alexa, set air conditioner to cool mode.
Alexa, set temperature at 22 degrees.
Alexa, set fan speed to auto.
Alexa, set air conditioner to sleep mode.
